  "title": "Lead Generation Specialist [ST]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Lead Generation Specialist</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p>\n<p><br>\nWe’re looking for a motivated and energetic individual to join our sales team as a Lead Generation Specialist. You will play a key role in connecting with potential customers, identifying opportunities, and supporting the sales team in closing deals.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proactively reach out to prospects via calls, emails, and digital platforms.</li>\n  <li>Research and map out potential target customers and industries.</li>\n  <li>Qualify and nurture leads, ensuring smooth handover to the sales team.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate lead information in the CRM system.</li>\n  <li>Communicate our value proposition effectively to generate interest.</li>\n  <li>Assist in arranging meetings and product demos for the sales team.</li>\n  <li>Track lead generation activities and share regular progress updates.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1–2 years’ experience in telesales, inside sales, or a related role. No experience but keen to take up the challenge can apply too!</li>\n  <li>Confident with outbound outreach and prospecting.</li>\n  <li>CRM familiarity is a plus, but not mandatory.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>✨ We value every application, but only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you for considering this opportunity.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</strong><br>\n <strong>EA Personnel: Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</strong></p>",
